cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with computer vision tasks such as object detection and scene retrieval, which are typically categorized under cs.CV. The use of unsupervised algorithms and Gaussian mixture models suggests a focus on machine learning and artificial intelligence, which are covered under cs.AI. The paper also discusses the evaluation of the proposed system, which falls under the purview of cs.LG (machine learning). The retrieval of suitable background scenes involves information retrieval techniques, which are covered under cs.IR. Finally, the paper mentions video composition, which is a multimedia application and falls under cs.MM.
